reviewText: One of the best instructional knitting craft series really good tips to learn I feel its a must have for me.
I really like the variety of projects shown, as well as the background info on the types of yarn!! The camera shots are very clear and the instruction is detailed!!
Excellent videos. I am an experienced knitter and there was still plenty of information that I could gleam from from them. Eunny Jang is Brilliant! I want to buy them all if I could afford to!
I haven't a knitting series of this caliber ever.  This is the best of the best.  I have become a very good knitter by just watching Eunny Jang's hands.  Recommend this for stages of knitters.
